TC_01,100percentpure,addItemToCart
Summary
Verify ability to add item to cart
Precondition:
Register a New User, username(Volodymyr), email(volodymyr.chyrva@yahoo.com), password(qwerty).
Successfully Log In.

Test Steps:
1. On My Account page Click on Search icon;
2. Enter "Target item" into search placeholder;
3. Press Enter;
4. On Search page click on "Target item";
5. Click "Add to tote";
6. Confirm "Target item" was added and visible;
Expected result :
Target Item placed in cart and visible .

