TC_7,100percentpure,Invalid Log In
Confirm User can not Log In with invalid credentials
Precondition:
Register a New User, username(Volodymyr), email(volodymyr.chyrva@yahoo.com), password(qwerty).

Test Steps:
1. On Login page Click 'Accept all cookies';
2. Hit "User" icon;
3. Enter invalid Password into "Password" placeholder;
4. Enter valid Email into "Email" placeholder;
5. Hit "Sign In";

Expected result :
My Account Page was not opened,Message "Incorrect email or password." appeared